      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That sounds good, but I've heard some mixed things from other donors about overhead being higher than advertised. Just to be 100% clear and for my own records, can you confirm the breakdown for my specific recent donation of $1M? I want to make sure the vast majority is hitting the ground in South Sudan and not just getting eaten up by HQ costs.",
